name: Honey Girl Organics
tag_list: skin-care, organic-skin-care, raw-honey, beeswax, skincare, natual, heal-skin, anti-aging
overview:
Honey Girl Organics offers you a line of natural skin care products handcrafted in Hawaii. These creams, toners, and balms are hand made from various blends of nature’s finest anti-aging ingredients. The combinations work together to heal and renew the skin, giving you a fresh, youthful appearance.

Our products are simple and pure, made from ingredients harvested from our holistically managed beehives on Oahu’s North Shore. They contain raw honey, beeswax, propolis, bee pollen, and organic extra virgin olive oil. Some of our skincare products also include purified water and various blends of essential oils to give them a pleasing fragrance and additional healing properties
